# ============================================================================
# Streamlit Secrets Template (for Community Cloud & local development)
#
# COMMUNITY CLOUD SETUP:
#   Go to your app dashboard → Settings → Secrets
#   Copy the contents of this file and paste into the Secrets manager.
#   Replace all placeholder values with your real API keys.
#
# LOCAL DEVELOPMENT:
#   Copy this file to secrets.toml (same directory) and fill in keys.
#   Streamlit auto-loads .streamlit/secrets.toml on startup.
#   Do NOT commit secrets.toml — it's already in .gitignore.
# ============================================================================

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# REQUIRED: At least one LLM provider API key
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
